Work in progress pipeline for dermatology textbook photograph race identification

Please import requirements.txt before using

Abd skin segmentation: https://github.com/MRE-Lab-UMD/abd-skin-segmentation/tree/master
Download Models/final_unet_pytorch.pth and create /models/abd-skin-segmentation/

paddle install: https://www.paddlepaddle.org.cn/install/quick?docurl=/documentation/docs/zh/develop/install/pip/windows-pip.html
Then pip install "paddleocr[all]"

